title: SYND 14-6-74 WEST GERMANY BEATS CHILE 1:0 IN WORLD CUP FOOTBALL MATCH IN WEST BERLIN
description:
(14 Jun 1972) **Clients are advised that clearance from FIFA may be required**

West Germany beats Chile 1:0 in world cup football match in West Berlin.
